				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">1) I think your number for wizard crit rate is low, although I don't have it written down offhand.
<br />

<br />
2) not removing crit rate and focusing from aggro generation tilts the numbers in the magician's favor.  (In reality the wizard has more aggroless bonus damage than the magician, your calculation actually penalizes the wizard for this)
<br />

<br />
3) I personally disagree that a gap of 68dps (~27%) with a tank who produces 200 hate/sec is acceptable, *especially* if there's a pet in use.
<br />

<br />
